<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Artyści uliczni na eventy | Spektakle uliczne i pokazy ognia</title>
<meta name="description" content="Artyści uliczni na eventy, festiwale i wydarzenia specjalne. Tworzymy spektakle uliczne, pokazy ognia i widowiska plenerowe w całej Polsce.">
<meta name="keywords" content="artyści uliczni, artyści uliczni na event, teatr uliczny, spektakl uliczny, pokazy ognia na event, atrakcje na festiwal, artyści na wydarzenia plenerowe, spektakle plenerowe">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --black:   #0a0a0a;
  --deep:    #111111;
  --card:    #181818;
  --red:     #c0161a;
  --red-hot: #e02020;
  --white:   #ffffff;
  --off:     #f0f0f0;
  --grey:    rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
  --muted:   rgba(255,255,255,0.48);
  --border:  rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  --border-r: rgba(192,22,26,0.35);
  --serif:   'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  --sans:    'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  background: var(--black);
  color: var(--white);
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.75;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   NAV
════════════════════════════════════════ */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 300;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  padding: 0.9rem 5vw;
  transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
}
nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(10,10,10,0.97);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

/* Logo — uses the actual PNG file */
.logo { display: flex; align-items: center; text-decoration: none; }
.logo img {
  height: 54px; width: auto;
  /* Make white logo visible on dark bg — logo has white text already */
  filter: brightness(1.1);
}

.nav-btn {
  font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--white); text-decoration: none;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--red); padding: 0.65rem 1.6rem;
  transition: all 0.25s;
}
.nav-btn:hover { background: var(--red); border-color: var(--red); }

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   HERO
════════════════════════════════════════ */
#hero {
  position: relative; min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-end; padding: 0 6vw 9vh;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Hero photo background */
.hero-bg {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: url('preview.webp') center 28% / cover no-repeat;
  background-color: #1a0505; /* fallback */
}
/* Layered overlay for readability — dark left side, subtle red top-left glow */
.hero-bg::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right,  rgba(5,5,5,0.93) 0%, rgba(5,5,5,0.6) 50%, rgba(5,5,5,0.5) 100%),
    linear-gradient(to top,    rgba(5,5,5,0.95) 0%, rgba(5,5,5,0.3) 55%, transparent 100%),
    linear-gradient(135deg,    rgba(140,8,8,0.22) 0%, transparent 40%);
}

.hero-tag {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
  font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--red); margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
  opacity: 0; animation: up 0.9s ease 0.3s forwards;
}
.hero-tag::before { content: ''; width: 2.5rem; height: 1px; background: var(--red); }

.hero-h1 {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 700;
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5.8vw, 5.5rem);
  line-height: 1.06; max-width: 14ch;
  color: var(--white);
  text-shadow: 0 2px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
  opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 0.48s forwards;
}
.hero-h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #ff4444; }

.hero-sub {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  margin-top: 1.8rem; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); max-width: 52ch;
  text-shadow: 0 1px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
  opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 0.7s forwards;
}

.hero-actions {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 2.8rem;
  opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 0.9s forwards;
}

.btn-red {
  display: inline-block; text-decoration: none;
  background: var(--red); color: #fff;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 1rem 2.4rem; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.25s;
}
.btn-red:hover { background: var(--red-hot); }

.btn-ghost {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  text-decoration: none; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
  font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
  transition: color 0.22s;
}
.btn-ghost:hover { color: #fff; }
.arr { display: inline-block; transition: transform 0.22s; }
.btn-ghost:hover .arr { transform: translateX(5px); }

.scroll-hint {
  position: absolute; bottom: 2.5rem; right: 5vw; z-index: 2;
  font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); writing-mode: vertical-rl;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
  animation: up 1s ease 1.3s both;
}
.scroll-hint::before {
  content: ''; width: 1px; height: 3.5rem;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--red), transparent);
  animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes scrollPulse { 0%,100%{opacity:.4} 50%{opacity:1} }
@keyframes up { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px)} to{opacity:1;transform:none} }

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   COMMON SECTION STYLES
════════════════════════════════════════ */
section { padding: 7rem 6vw; }
.inner { max-width: 1180px; }

.label {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
  font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--red); margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}
.label::before { content: ''; width: 1.8rem; height: 1px; background: var(--red); }

h2 {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 700;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.8vw, 3.1rem); line-height: 1.12;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--white);
}
h2 em { font-style: italic; color: #ff4444; }

.lead {
  font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--grey); line-height: 1.85;
  max-width: 60ch; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; font-weight: 300;
}
.body-text {
  font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.85;
  max-width: 60ch; margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
}

/* Section separator lines */
.sep {
  width: 100%; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--border), transparent);
}
.sep-red {
  width: 100%; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(192,22,26,0.5), transparent);
}

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   O NAS
════════════════════════════════════════ */
#onas { background: var(--deep); }
.onas-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6vw;
  align-items: center;
}
.tag-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
.tag {
  font-size: 0.67rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  transition: all 0.22s;
}
.tag:hover { border-color: var(--red); color: var(--red); }

.quote-box {
  background: var(--card); border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
  padding: 3rem 2.6rem; position: relative;
}
.quote-box::before {
  content: '\201C'; font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 9rem; line-height: 0.5;
  color: var(--red); opacity: 0.1;
  position: absolute; top: 2rem; left: 1.5rem; pointer-events: none;
}
.quote-box blockquote {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.35rem;
  font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--white); position: relative; z-index: 1;
}

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   STATS / FIRE
════════════════════════════════════════ */
#stats { background: var(--black); padding: 6rem 6vw; }

.stats-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 3rem;
}

.stat-card {
  background: #130000;
  border: 1px solid rgba(192,22,26,0.3);
  padding: 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  min-height: 300px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
}
.stat-card:hover { border-color: var(--red); transform: translateY(-4px); }

.fire-wrap {
  position: relative; width: 100%; flex: 1;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  min-height: 220px;
}

.fire-canvas {
  position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
  opacity: 0.85;
}

.stat-num {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 700;
  font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 6rem);
  color: #fff;
  text-shadow:
    0 0 20px rgba(255,80,0,0.9),
    0 0 40px rgba(255,120,0,0.6),
    0 0 80px rgba(200,20,0,0.4);
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.stat-label {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  width: 100%; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
  font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  text-align: center;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(192,22,26,0.3);
  background: rgba(10,0,0,0.6);
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
}

@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .stat-card { min-height: 220px; }
}

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   REALIZACJE
════════════════════════════════════════ */
#realizacje { background: var(--black); }

.cards-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  margin-top: 3.5rem;
}
.card {
  background: var(--black); padding: 2.5rem;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: background 0.25s;
}
.card:hover { background: var(--card); }
.card::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
  background: var(--red); transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
  transition: transform 0.35s ease;
}
.card:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
.card-icon { font-size: 1.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; display: block; }
.card h4 {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
}
.card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.75; }

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   ELASTYCZNOŚĆ
════════════════════════════════════════ */
#elastycznosc { background: var(--deep); }
.elast-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.25fr; gap: 7vw; align-items: start;
}
.steps { margin-top: 2.5rem; }
.step {
  display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; padding: 1.7rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); transition: border-color 0.22s;
}
.step:first-child { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
.step:hover { border-color: var(--border-r); }
.step-num {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2.1rem; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--red); line-height: 1; min-width: 2.2rem;
}
.step-body h5 {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
}
.step-body p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; }

.box {
  background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border-r);
  padding: 3.5rem; position: relative;
}
.box::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute;
  top: -1px; left: 3rem; right: 3rem; height: 2px; background: var(--red);
}
.box h3 {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.65rem; font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.22; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}
.box .btn-red { margin-top: 1.4rem; display: inline-block; }

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   KONTAKT
════════════════════════════════════════ */
#kontakt {
  background: var(--black); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
#kontakt::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: -20%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 700px; height: 700px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(192,22,26,0.08) 0%, transparent 65%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.kontakt-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr; gap: 7vw;
  align-items: start; position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.phone-block {
  margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}
.phone-block p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
.phone-link {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--red); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  display: block; transition: color 0.22s;
}
.phone-link:hover { color: var(--red-hot); }

/* Form */
.form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; }
.field { position: relative; }
.field input, .field textarea {
  width: 100%; background: #161616; border: none; outline: none;
  color: var(--white); font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 300;
  font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 1.35rem 1.5rem; transition: background 0.22s;
}
.field input::placeholder, .field textarea::placeholder {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.28); font-size: 0.74rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.field input:focus, .field textarea:focus { background: #1f1010; }
.field textarea { min-height: 130px; resize: vertical; }
.field-bar {
  position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px;
  background: var(--red); transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
  transition: transform 0.36s ease;
}
.field:focus-within .field-bar { transform: scaleX(1); }
.form-submit .btn-red { width: 100%; text-align: center; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
.form-note { margin-top: 1.2rem; font-size: 0.73rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.28); line-height: 1.7; }

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   FOOTER
════════════════════════════════════════ */
footer {
  padding: 2.5rem 6vw; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem;
}
footer img { height: 40px; width: auto; opacity: 0.7; }
.footer-copy { font-size: 0.66rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); text-transform: uppercase; }

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   REVEAL ANIMATION
════════════════════════════════════════ */
.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
.reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

/* ════════════════════════════════════════
   RESPONSIVE
════════════════════════════════════════ */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .onas-grid, .elast-grid, .kontakt-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .quote-box { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .box { padding: 2.5rem 2rem; }
  section { padding: 5rem 5vw; }
  .hero-h1 { font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 9vw, 3.5rem); }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ════ NAV ════ -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#" class="logo">
    <img src="ArtysciUliczniKrakowaLogoOPT.png" alt="Artyści Uliczni Krakowa">
  </a>
  <a href="#kontakt" class="nav-btn">Zapytaj o wycenę</a>
</nav>

<!-- ════ HERO ════ -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>

  <p class="hero-tag">Spektakle · Teatr Uliczny · Pokazy Ognia</p>

  <h1 class="hero-h1">
    My nie tworzymy produktu.<br>
    My tworzymy <em>przeżycie</em>,<br>
    które zostaje z Tobą.
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-sub">
    Artyści uliczni na eventy, festiwale i wydarzenia specjalne. Tworzymy spektakle uliczne,
    pokazy ognia, happeningi i widowiska plenerowe dla miast, firm oraz organizatorów wydarzeń
    na terenie całej Polski.
  </p>

  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#kontakt" class="btn-red">Porozmawiajmy o Twoim wydarzeniu</a>
    <a href="#realizacje" class="btn-ghost">Zobacz co robimy <span class="arr">→</span></a>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-hint">Przewiń</div>
</section>

<div class="sep-red"></div>

<!-- ════ O NAS ════ -->
<section id="onas">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="onas-grid">
      <div>
        <p class="label">O nas</p>
        <h2>Coś więcej niż <em>atrakcja</em></h2>
        <p class="lead">Jeśli szukasz czegoś więcej niż atrakcji na wydarzenie — jesteś we właściwym miejscu.</p>
        <p class="body-text">Nasze spektakle łączą teatr uliczny, sztukę performatywną, widowisko plenerowe i interakcję z publicznością. Każde wydarzenie traktujemy jak osobną historię.</p>
        <p class="body-text">Tworzymy emocje, które zostają z widzami jeszcze długo po zakończeniu spektaklu.</p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">Teatr uliczny</span>
          <span class="tag">Sztuka performatywna</span>
          <span class="tag">Widowisko plenerowe</span>
          <span class="tag">Interakcja z publicznością</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-box reveal">
        <blockquote>
          Każde wydarzenie traktujemy jak osobną historię — unikalną, niepowtarzalną i głęboko ludzką.
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ STATS ════ -->
<section id="stats">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="label">Dlaczego warto nam zaufać?</p>
    <div class="stats-grid">

      <div class="stat-card reveal">
        <div class="fire-wrap">
          <canvas class="fire-canvas" data-index="0"></canvas>
          <span class="stat-num" data-target="20" data-suffix="">0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="stat-label">Lat doświadczenia</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card reveal">
        <div class="fire-wrap">
          <canvas class="fire-canvas" data-index="1"></canvas>
          <span class="stat-num" data-target="462" data-suffix="+">0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="stat-label">Zrealizowanych oryginalnych imprez</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card reveal">
        <div class="fire-wrap">
          <canvas class="fire-canvas" data-index="2"></canvas>
          <span class="stat-num" data-target="1" data-suffix="">0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="stat-label">Ogromny chaos — zawsze pod kontrolą</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="sep"></div>

<!-- ════ REALIZACJE ════ -->
<section id="realizacje">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="label">Nasze realizacje</p>
    <h2>Artyści uliczni na eventy i <em>festiwale</em></h2>
    <p class="lead" style="max-width:66ch;">Artyści uliczni to wyjątkowa forma atrakcji podczas wydarzeń plenerowych, festiwali miejskich, imprez firmowych oraz eventów specjalnych. Działamy na terenie całej Polski.</p>

    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card reveal"><span class="card-icon">🎭</span><h4>Spektakle uliczne</h4><p>Profesjonalne widowiska dla szerokiej publiczności, łączące narrację z wizualnym spektaklem i żywą interakcją.</p></div>
      <div class="card reveal"><span class="card-icon">🔥</span><h4>Pokazy ognia</h4><p>Efektowne i bezpieczne pokazy ognia — idealne na wieczorne imprezy plenerowe i prestiżowe eventy firmowe.</p></div>
